### Self-host deployment
# Real secrets live here. Ignore the live file plus any temp/backup variants
# (.tmp, .bak, dated copies) the install/backup scripts may write — but keep
# tracking the committed template. .dockerignore already excludes the same set.
.env.selfhost
.env.selfhost.*
!.env.selfhost.example
backups/

